{
  "clauseId": "6bf714e185a74ae2ad7571027a141da9",
  "clauseName": "2.1.1.1_农产品精简版V3.0-new（20260414165344）",
  "clauseNumber": "2.1.1.1",
  "clauseContent": "2.1.1.1.  发票类型与抵扣规则\n<div class=\"quill-better-table-wrapper\"><table class=\"quill-better-table\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><colgroup><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-row=\"1\"><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">发票类型</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">销售方身份/业务性质</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">购买方抵扣规则</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">关键条件与风险提示</strong></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"2\"><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"2\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">农产品销售发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（1）数电免税普票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">自产自销</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">按票面金额×9%计算抵扣【票面金额通常是指不含税金额，但是免税情形下，票面金额和含税金额也是相等的，不需要做价税分离】</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"5\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">发票左上角必须有&nbsp;“自产农产品销售”&nbsp;标签，否则无法勾选抵扣。这是最大风险点！</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"3\"><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（2）税控系统开具的免税普票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">自产自销</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">按票面金额×9%计算抵扣</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">无标签要求，但需通过“待处理农产品发票”模块预处理后勾选。需确保业务实质为自产。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"4\"><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（3）税务机关代开的免税普票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">自然人自产自销</span></p></td><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">按票面金额×9%计算抵扣</span></p></td><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">若为数电票，同样需要“自产农产品销售”标签；非数电票则需在“代开农产品发票录入”模块补录信息。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"5\"><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（4）农产品收购发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">购买方向农业生产者个人收购自产农产品时自行开具</span></p></td><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">按票面金额×9%计算抵扣</span></p></td><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">发票需注明“收购”或“农产品收购”字样。一般只限本县（市、区）范围内开具。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"6\"><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（5）3%增值税专用发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">小规模纳税人（不区分是否自产）</span></p></td><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">按票面金额×9%计算抵扣</span></p></td><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">需先在“待处理农产品发票”模块处理。这是最有利的专票类型，可实现“低征高扣”。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"7\"><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（6）1%&nbsp;增值税专用发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">小规模纳税人（不区分是否自产）</span></p></td><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">只能按票面注明的1%税额抵扣，不能按9%计算抵扣</span></p></td><td data-row=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"7\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">常见误区：很多企业误以为1%专票也能按9%抵扣，这是严重错误！</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"8\"><td data-row=\"8\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"8\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（7）9%增值税专用发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"8\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"8\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">一般纳税人（不区分是否自产）</span></p></td><td data-row=\"8\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"8\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">按票面注明的9%税额进行抵扣</span></p></td><td data-row=\"8\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"8\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">常规凭票抵扣，无特殊计算。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"9\"><td data-row=\"9\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"9\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（8）海关进口增值税专用缴款书</span></p></td><td data-row=\"9\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"9\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">进口农产品</span></p></td><td data-row=\"9\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"9\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">按缴款书注明的增值税额抵扣</span></p></td><td data-row=\"9\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"9\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">——</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"10\"><td data-row=\"10\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"10\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（9）流通环节免税普票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"10\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"10\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">批发、零售免税蔬菜/鲜活肉蛋/种子种苗的纳税人</span></p></td><td data-row=\"10\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"10\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">不得抵扣</span></p></td><td data-row=\"10\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"10\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">这是最容易被误抵扣的发票！此类发票用于已享受免税的流通环节，进项税不得抵扣。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"11\"><td data-row=\"11\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"11\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（10）带税率的普通发票</span></p></td><td data-row=\"11\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"11\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">任何纳税人（如小规模纳税人开具1%/3%普票）</span></p></td><td data-row=\"11\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"11\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">不得抵扣</span></p></td><td data-row=\"11\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"11\" data-cell=\"4\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">普通发票无论税率多少，均不能作为进项抵扣凭证。必须取得专用发票、农产品销售发票（自产自销）、农产品收购发票、海关进口增值税专用缴款书才可以抵扣进项税额。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
